            <div class="card hoverable">
              <div class="card-content">
                <span class="card-title">Spring Boot gRPC</span>
                <p>This project demonstrates a modular microservice setup built with Spring Boot and gRPC.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="card-action">
                <a href="https://github.com/mandeep111/grpc_demo" target="_blank">View on GitHub</a>
              </div>
